# Battle for Wesnoth

[[!img wesnoth-logo.png alt="Battle for Wesnoth logo" class="projectlogo" link="no"]]

[Battle for Wesnoth](https://www.wesnoth.org/) is an open source, turn-based strategy game with a high fantasy theme. It features both singleplayer and online/hotseat multiplayer combat. The game also allows its users to create their own "campaigns" and make them publicly available, as well as collaborating with the core team to expand the open source gaming ecosystem.

